### 7. Búsqueda POST con payload completo
POST http://localhost:3000/addresses/search/proximity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "Carrera 15 #25-30 Barrio Centro",
  "options": {
    "searchRadius": 20,
    "includeNeighborhoods": true,
    "includeQuadrants": false,
    "exactMatch": false
  }
}

